WEBVTT

00:08.760 --> 00:09.600
Chu Meng

00:11.240 --> 00:13.120
Summon the second son to see me

00:29.840 --> 00:30.440
Father

00:30.720 --> 00:32.880
I've almost defeated those remnants in Yan Bei

00:33.640 --> 00:35.040
Why call me back at this time?

00:42.760 --> 00:46.080
Father, how is your wound?

00:59.320 --> 01:00.040
Father

01:02.080 --> 01:05.480
I've thought for a long time

01:06.440 --> 01:07.480
I've decided

01:08.040 --> 01:09.840
To pass the throne to your elder brother

01:10.760 --> 01:11.520
Father

01:12.240 --> 01:13.000
Father

01:13.800 --> 01:15.040
Since I was young, when you told me to go east

01:15.560 --> 01:16.560
I never went west

01:17.200 --> 01:18.120
You said to recover lost territories

01:18.720 --> 01:20.440
I trained in martial arts and studied military texts

01:20.440 --> 01:21.480
Just to help you

01:21.760 --> 01:22.440
After the northern expedition

01:22.800 --> 01:24.400
I always led from the front in every battle

01:25.000 --> 01:25.880
Because I know

01:26.360 --> 01:27.880
Only our Sikong family doesn't fear death

01:28.360 --> 01:29.240
The brothers under me

01:29.720 --> 01:31.200
Will truly fight with all their might

01:33.640 --> 01:37.560
Father, I never thought to compete with elder brother

01:40.160 --> 01:41.680
I just wanted to be a good son

01:43.440 --> 01:47.480
Second son, you are most like me

01:49.440 --> 01:49.960
Father

01:56.800 --> 01:58.720
But for Xuan Kingdom's future

02:00.720 --> 02:01.240
I

02:02.680 --> 02:03.720
Cannot keep you

02:05.640 --> 02:06.200
Father

02:13.720 --> 02:14.480
My son

02:20.040 --> 02:20.600
My son

02:22.520 --> 02:23.200
I understand

03:19.760 --> 03:20.560
Xu'er

03:21.440 --> 03:21.960
Xu'er

03:23.840 --> 03:24.480
Xu'er

03:26.640 --> 03:28.160
It was never your fault

03:31.080 --> 03:33.560
It was my fault as a father

03:37.680 --> 03:39.040
I'm sorry, my son

03:41.840 --> 03:43.480
I'm sorry, my son

03:44.720 --> 03:45.840
After we get there

03:48.080 --> 03:49.640
I'll make it up to you

03:51.200 --> 03:55.680
Then we two will ride horses together

03:57.520 --> 03:58.600
Fish together

04:00.360 --> 04:01.640
Hunt together
